
                            [41m[32m CIRCUS ATTRACTIONS [0m


[1mLOADING INSTRUCTIONS[0m
AMIGA:         Insert disk 1 in drive dfO when the Workbench is desired.

[1mTRAMPOLINING[0m
[3mThe aim is to jump as high as possible, attempting somersaults etc and collecting
bonus symbols.[0m
Joystick up/down: Bouncing on trampoline or in the air legs pulled up or
stretched.
Joystick left: Forward somersault.
Joystick right: Backward somersault.
 with fire button pressed: slow somersault momentum.
Two-players-mode - The jump movements are individually controlled.

[1mTIGHTROPE WALKING[0m
[3mKeep your balance.[0m
Joystick left/right: Balance
Joystick left up/right up : Extreme balance
Fire button: scissorkick
Fire button + joystick up: Backwards somersault
Fire button + joystick down: Handstand.
Two-players-mode - One balancing woman stands on the shoulders of the
other. Only the lady on top can attempt the artistic acts.

[1mJUGGLING[0m
[3mAim is to juggle as long as possble.[0m
Fire button: Accept item from assistant
Joystick left: Throw ball with left hand
Joystick down : Kick ball with left foot
Joystick up: Jump
Joystick right: Throw club with left hand
Two-players-mode - Both players throw balls at each other.

[1mKNIFE THROWING[0m
[3mYou direct a crosshair with the joystick showing you the point where the knife is going
to.[0m
Joystick in all directions: Control crosshair
Fire button: Take a knife
Release fire button: Throw knife Two-player-mode
Both players throw knives at the same rotating disk.

[1mJUMPING CLOWNS[0m
[3mJump as high as possible from one seesaw to the other, collect bonus items and keep
the audience's delight.[0m
Joystick left up/right up: High jump into the air
Joystick left/right: medium-high flight
Joystick down left/down right: low jump during the flight
Joystick left/right: adjust flight
Fire button: The clown on the target seesaw changes sides on the seesaw.
Two-players-mode - Two players control a jumping clown each in turns,
during the other player may change sides on the seesaw under the
abovementioned conditions.


